{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898931920,"sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd3307a001wzz7r59o3SsX1x","messageID":"msg_d7bd3268e001u4VxmAyUheQGep","sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d91ff4eea11d472587d62b5a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/tasks/ar-030-tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/tasks/ar-030-tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n2: \n3: **Module**: manifests  \n4: **Language**: YAML  \n5: **Size**: L  \n6: **Status**: ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Tasks\n11: \n12: ### T001: Chart metadata and directory structure\n13: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/` directory structure\n14: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/Chart.yaml` with metadata\n15: - [ ] Verify `apiVersion: v2`, `type: application`, `version: 1.0.0`, `appVersion: \"1.0.0\"`\n16: - [ ] Verify keywords: `agentcube`, `ai`, `code-interpreter`, `agent-runtime`, `kubernetes`\n17: - [ ] Verify maintainers list with name and email fields\n18: - [ ] Verify home URL: `https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n19: \n20: ### T002: Default values.yaml - Global and common settings\n21: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values.yaml` file\n22: - [ ] Define `global` section with `imageRegistry`, `imagePullSecrets`, `namespaceOverride`, `labels`, `annotations`\n23: - [ ] Define top-level `imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent`\n24: - [ ] Define `rbac` section with `create: true` and `clusterRole` rules\n25: - [ ] Define `priorityClassName` and `extraManifests` settings\n26: - [ ] Verify default values match design specification\n27: \n28: ### T003: Values.yaml - Controller Manager configuration\n29: - [ ] Add `controllerManager` section to `values.yaml`\n30: - [ ] Configure `enabled: true`, `replicaCount: 2`\n31: - [ ] Define image settings: repository `agentcube/controller-manager`, tag `v1.0.0`\n32: - [ ] Define service settings: type `ClusterIP`, port `8080`, targetPort `8080`\n33: - [ ] Define resource requests: cpu `100m`, memory `128Mi`\n34: - [ ] Define resource limits: cpu `500m`, memory `512Mi`\n35: - [ ] Configure security contexts: runAsNonRoot `true`, runAsUser `1000`, fsGroup `1000`\n36: - [ ] Configure container security contexts: allowPrivilegeEscalation `false`, capabilities drop `ALL`\n37: - [ ] Configure livenessProbe: httpGet path `/healthz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `30`\n38: - [ ] Configure readinessProbe: httpGet path `/readyz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `10`\n39: - [ ] Configure autoscaling: enabled `false`, minReplicas `2`, maxReplicas `5`, targetCPU `80%`\n40: - [ ] Configure podDisruptionBudget: enabled `true`, minAvailable `1`\n41: - [ ] Configure serviceAccount: create `true`, name `\"\"`\n42: - [ ] Configure rbac: create `true`, rules `[]`\n43: \n44: ### T004: Values.yaml - Workload Manager configuration\n45: - [ ] Add `workloadManager` section to `values.yaml`\n46: - [ ] Configure `enabled: true`, `replicaCount: 2`\n47: - [ ] Define image settings: repository `agentcube/workload-manager`, tag `v1.0.0`\n48: - [ ] Define service settings: type `ClusterIP`, port `8080`, targetPort `8080`\n49: - [ ] Define resource requests: cpu `200m`, memory `256Mi`\n50: - [ ] Define resource limits: cpu `1000m`, memory `1Gi`\n51: - [ ] Configure security contexts matching Controller Manager\n52: - [ ] Configure livenessProbe: httpGet path `/healthz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `30`\n53: - [ ] Configure readinessProbe: httpGet path `/readyz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `10`\n54: - [ ] Configure autoscaling: enabled `false`, minReplicas `2`, maxReplicas `10`, targetCPU `75%`\n55: - [ ] Configure podDisruptionBudget: enabled `true`, minAvailable `1`\n56: - [ ] Configure serviceAccount: create `true`, name `\"\"`\n57: - [ ] Configure rbac: create `true`, rules `[]`\n58: \n59: ### T005: Values.yaml - Router configuration\n60: - [ ] Add `router` section to `values.yaml`\n61: - [ ] Configure `enabled: true`, `replicaCount: 3`\n62: - [ ] Define image settings: repository `agentcube/router`, tag `v1.0.0`\n63: - [ ] Define service settings: type `ClusterIP`, port `8080`, targetPort `8080`\n64: - [ ] Define resource requests: cpu `150m`, memory `192Mi`\n65: - [ ] Define resource limits: cpu `750m`, memory `768Mi`\n66: - [ ] Configure podAntiAffinity: requiredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution\n67: - [ ] Configure security contexts matching other components\n68: - [ ] Configure livenessProbe: httpGet path `/healthz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `30`\n69: - [ ] Configure readinessProbe: httpGet path `/readyz`, port `8080`, initialDelaySeconds `10`\n70: - [ ] Configure autoscaling: enabled `false`, minReplicas `3`, maxReplicas `10`, targetCPU `70%`\n71: - [ ] Configure podDisruptionBudget: enabled `true`, minAvailable `2`\n72: - [ ] Configure ingress: enabled `false`, className `nginx`, hosts list\n73: - [ ] Configure serviceAccount: create `true`, name `\"\"`\n74: \n75: ### T006: Values.yaml - Monitoring and additional configurations\n76: - [ ] Add `monitoring` section with `enabled: false`\n77: - [ ] Configure `serviceMonitor`: enabled `false`, interval `30s`, scrapeTimeout `10s`\n78: - [ ] Configure `prometheusRule`: enabled `false`\n79: - [ ] Add `configMaps` section with `agentcubeConfig.create: true`\n80: - [ ] Define config data: LOG_LEVEL `info`, LOG_FORMAT `json`, METRICS_ENABLED `true`, METRICS_PORT `9090`\n81: - [ ] Add `secrets` section with `create: false`, name `agentcube-secrets`\n82: - [ ] Add `networkPolicies` section with `enabled: false`, defaultDeny `false`\n83: - [ ] Add `ingress` section with `enabled: false`, className `nginx`, tls settings\n84: - [ ] Add `hooks` section with preInstall, postInstall, preUpgrade, postUpgrade\n85: \n86: ### T007: Environment-specific values files\n87: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values-dev.yaml`\n88: - [ ] Set development-specific overrides (e.g., lower resource limits, debug enabled)\n89: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values-prod.yaml`\n90: - [ ] Set production-specific overrides (e.g., higher resource limits, monitoring enabled)\n91: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/values-test.yaml`\n92: - [ ] Set test-specific overrides (e.g., single replica, minimal resources)\n93: \n94: ### T008: Template helpers (_helpers.tpl)\n95: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n96: - [ ] Define `agentcube.name` helper with truncation to 63 chars\n97: - [ ] Define `agentcube.fullname` helper with release name handling\n98: - [ ] Define `agentcube.chart` helper for chart labels\n99: - [ ] Define `agentcube.labels` helper with common labels\n100: - [ ] Define `agentcube.selectorLabels` helper for pod selectors\n101: - [ ] Define `agentcube.controllerManager.serviceAccountName` helper\n102: - [ ] Define `agentcube.workloadManager.serviceAccountName` helper\n103: - [ ] Define `agentcube.router.serviceAccountName` helper\n104: - [ ] Define `agentcube.imageRegistry` helper\n105: - [ ] Define `agentcube.image` helper for full image reference\n106: - [ ] Verify all helpers follow Helm best practices\n107: \n108: ### T009: CRD templates - AgentRuntime\n109: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/crds/` directory\n110: - [ ] Create `agentruntime.yaml` CRD template\n111: - [ ] Verify API version: `apiextensions.k8s.io/v1`\n112: - [ ] Verify CRD name: `agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n113: - [ ] Verify helm hook annotations: `crd-install`, hook-weight `-5`\n114: - [ ] Verify group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, kind: `AgentRuntime`, scope: `Namespaced`\n115: - [ ] Verify version: `v1alpha1`, served `true`, storage `true`\n116: - [ ] Verify spec schema with required fields: maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, podTemplate, targetPort\n117: - [ ] Verify status schema with conditions subresource\n118: - [ ] Verify additionalPrinterColumns for Age\n119: \n120: ### T010: CRD templates - CodeInterpreter\n121: - [ ] Create `codeinterpreter.yaml` CRD template\n122: - [ ] Verify API version: `apiextensions.k8s.io/v1`\n123: - [ ] Verify CRD name: `codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n124: - [ ] Verify helm hook annotations: `crd-install`, hook-weight `-5`\n125: - [ ] Verify group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, kind: `CodeInterpreter`, scope: `Namespaced`\n126: - [ ] Verify version: `v1alpha1`, served `true`, storage `true`\n127: - [ ] Verify spec schema with all required fields\n128: - [ ] Verify status schema with conditions subresource\n129: - [ ] Verify additionalPrinterColumns for Age\n130: \n131: ### T011: Controller Manager deployment template\n132: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/controller-manager/deployment.yaml`\n133: - [ ] Verify condition: `{{- if .Values.controllerManager.enabled }}`\n134: - [ ] Verify Deployment API version: `apps/v1`\n135: - [ ] Verify name uses `agentcube.fullname` helper\n136: - [ ] Verify namespace uses `agentcube.namespace` helper\n137: - [ ] Verify labels include component: `controller-manager`\n138: - [ ] Verify replicas from `controllerManager.replicaCount`\n139: - [ ] Verify selector matches component labels\n140: - [ ] Verify serviceAccountName uses helper\n141: - [ ] Verify image uses `agentcube.image` helper with correct parameters\n142: - [ ] Verify container args: `--leader-elect`, `--health-probe-bind-address=:8080`, `--metrics-bind-address=:9090`\n143: - [ ] Verify container ports: http `8080`, metrics `9090`\n144: - [ ] Verify livenessProbe and readinessProbe from values\n145: - [ ] Verify resources from values\n146: - [ ] Verify security contexts from values\n147: - [ ] Verify checksum/config annotation for ConfigMap changes\n148: \n149: ### T012: Controller Manager service template\n150: - [ ] Create `manifests/charts/agentcube/templates/controller-manager/service.yaml`\n151: - [ ] Verify condition: `{{- if .Values.controllerManager.enabled }}`\n1