leted\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. Architecture\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\\n6: \\n7: This AR covers comprehensive Go unit tests for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module, including handler, middleware, reconciler, response sub-packages and top-level constants.\\n8: \\n9: ### 1.2 System Context\\n10: \\n11: ```\\n12: pkg/workloadmanager/\\n13: ├── const.go              # Constants/enums\\n14: ├── const_test.go         # NEW — constant validation tests\\n15: ├── handler/\\n16: │   ├── *.go              # HTTP handlers\\n17: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — handler tests\\n18: ├── middleware/\\n19: │   ├── *.go              # HTTP middleware\\n20: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — middleware tests\\n21: ├── reconciler/\\n22: │   ├── *.go              # State reconciler\\n23: │   └── *_test.go         # NEW — reconciler tests\\n24: └── response/\\n25:     ├── *.go              # Response utilities\\n26:     └── *_test.go         # NEW — response tests\\n27: ```\\n28: \\n29: ### 1.3 Design Principles\\n30: \\n31: - **Table-driven tests**: Go idiom for test data organization\\n32: - **No production code changes**: Only `*_test.go` additions\\n33: - **httptest for handlers**: `net/http/httptest` for HTTP handler testing\\n34: - **Interface-based mocking**: Abstract external dependencies behind interfaces\\n35: - **Black-box + white-box**: Mix of `package_test`... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897375451,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28444dcffffeVsazahFTZhj6mv\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbb6719001GUIzqc4A4e09Ug\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbb3db5001xO4Foc1GbRCaEH\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28444dcfff