-->\\n52: \\n53: ## Acceptance Criteria\\n54: \\n55: <!-- TODO: Define measurable acceptance criteria. -->\\n56: \\n57: - [ ] Criterion 1\\n58: - [ ] Criterion 2\\n... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897439952,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc69ac001cjW2hRQ4stDcNm\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc555b001oUNzNs9bIrVvIT\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_301d26332bf042f78cf8d47e\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-041/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-041 — E2E 集成测试\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** test/e2e\\n4: **Language:** Go\\n5: **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube 平台建立端到端（E2E）集成测试套件，在真实 Kind Kubernetes 集群中验证核心业务流程的完整性。覆盖 client-go 客户端库的 CRUD 操作、sandbox 全生命周期（创建→路由→状态查询→TTL 续期→删除）、以及 Helm 部署后的组件健康检查。目标是确保各组件（router、workloadmanager、agentd、CRD controller）在集成场景下协同工作正常，为 CI/CD 流水线提供可靠的发布门禁。\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: 1. **test/e2e/framework/** — E2E 测试框架与工具\\n16:    - Kind 集群管理（创建/销毁/加载镜像）\\n17:    - Helm chart 安装/卸载封装\\n18:    - client-go Clientset 初始化\\n19:    - 测试命名空间隔离与清理\\n20:    - 断言辅助函数（Eventually、Consistently 风格的轮询断言）\\n21: \\n22: 2. **test/e2e/clientgo/** — client-go 库 E2E 测试\\n23:    - AgentRuntime CRUD 完整流程（Create → Get → List → Update → UpdateStatus → Patch → Delete）\\n24:    - CodeInterpreter CRUD 完整流程\\n25:    - Informer 同步验证（创建资源后 informer 能正确收到事件）\\n26:    - Lister 缓存一致性验证\\n27:    - Fake client 与真实集群行为一致性抽查\\n28: \\n29: 3. **test/e2e/sandbox/** — Sandbox 生命周期 E2E 测试\\n30:    - 通过 workloadmanager API 创建 AgentRuntime sandbox（POST /api/v1/sandboxes）\\n31:    - Sandbox 状态查询（GET /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID）\\n32:    - Sandbox 列表（GET /api/v1/sandboxes）\\n33:    - TTL 续期（POST /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID/extend）\\n34:    - Sandbox 删除（DELETE /api/v1/sandboxes/:sessionID）\\n35:    - 创建后 Pod 启动与 IP 分配验证\\n36:    - Sandbox 过期后自动清理验证（依赖 agentd）\\n37: \\n38: 4. **test/... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897441409,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc6f5e001GQuY8QTldxP90K\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc555b001oUNzNs9bIrVvIT\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_1c2de8eb3a334f0195f89039\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-038/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\\n4: **Language:** Go\\n5: **Size:** L\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块补齐缺失的 Go 单元测试，覆盖 reconciler 核心协调逻辑、handler sandbox 创建流程、及顶层常量定义。已有测试（response、lifecycle、delete、metrics）保持不变。目标是提升关键路径代码覆盖率、防止回归、为后续重构提供安全网。\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: 1. **reconciler/reconciler_test.go** — `SandboxReconciler` 生命周期测试\\n16:    - `NewSandboxReconciler` 参数校验（nil Store/Clientset/InformerFactory panic）\\n17:    - `Run` 幂等性（重复调用忽略）、cache sync 成功/失败路径\\n18:    - `Enqueue` key 格式（带/不带 namespace）、metrics 触发\\n19:    - `WatchSandboxOnce` 正常返回、超时返回\\n20: \\n21: 2. **reconciler/sync_test.go** — 工作队列与 sync 流程测试\\n22:    - `syncHandler` key 解析（有效/无效格式）\\n23:    - AgentRuntime 存在 → `reconcileAgentRuntime`\\n24:    - CodeInterpreter 存在 → `reconcileCodeInterpreter`\\n25:    - Pod 存在 → `reconcilePod`\\n26:    - 三者均不存在 → 返回 nil\\n27:    - `processNextWorkItem` 重试逻辑（maxRetries=15、指数退避、超时强制退出）\\n28:    - `determineResourceType` 根据 lister 结果推断资源类型\\n29: \\n30: 3. **reconciler/agentruntime_test.go** — AgentRuntime 协调测试\\n31:    - `mapConditionToStatus` 条件映射（Ready=True→running、Ready=False+Terminated→terminated、Ready=False→pending、Ready=Unknown→pending、无条件→pending）\\n32:    - `reconcileAgentRuntime` 正常路径：lister 获取 → session-id 标签 → Store 不存在则 StoreSandbox、存在且状态变化则 Update... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n13: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775897441525,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc608b0015fJK0RiteOLVLD\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc555b001oUNzNs9bIrVvIT\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"There's already an AR-042 proposal. Let me read it and a recent one for format reference.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775897441523,\"end\":1775897441523}}}\n14: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897441559,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc74f60015CgsSQ94fPtt7G\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc555b001oUNzNs9bIrVvIT\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":23488,\"input\":23191,\"output\":253,\"reasoning\":44,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.006891063}}\n15: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897445007,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc8289001I8HbIghv8xoGxq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc7535001U1o1xiLTqs4WaA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897447116,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc86ea001P35p7D1XPk71ba\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc7535001U1o1xiLTqs4WaA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_59d5ff5c37d5426fac67e8c4\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\\n34:   Sand... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897448560,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc8b9b0014M9n73shae75Tf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc7535001U1o1xiLTqs4WaA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_1ea17f0a67524ea898b5b883\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\",\"pattern\":\"docs/**/*\"},\"output\":\"No files found\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775897448547,\"end\":1775897448558}}}}\n18: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775897448650,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc85cf0016zd15YRq7A2sB4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc7535001U1o1xiLTqs4WaA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Let me also check the project context and existing docs module.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775897448648,\"end\":1775897448648}}}\n19: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897448677,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc90cb001g1L5q4HSX2kWNA\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc7535001U1o1xiLTqs4WaA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":34573,\"input\":34372,\"output\":161,\"reasoning\":40,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.009818523}}\n20: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897452684,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbca088001i3TJho1RRA4v8J\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc90fb001qZJuu6w2F2bNaN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n21: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775897520922,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbcada8001QZoGHFMeEztubA\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc90fb001qZJuu6w2F2bNaN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have full context. Let me write the proposal.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775897520921,\"end\":1775897520921}}}\n22: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897520941,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbcaec0001YBLmBcxrlKQM7l\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc90fb001qZJuu6w2F2bNaN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_eaab0e5a205d451ca96b09e1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\\n\\n**Module:** docs\\n**Language:** TypeScript\\n**Size:** M\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。当前项目文档散落在各模块的 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 等文件中，缺乏统一的导航、搜索和版本管理能力。目标是提供一个可本地预览、可 CI 构建、可部署到 GitHub Pages 的结构化文档站，降低新贡献者的入门门槛，提升项目可维护性。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **docs/ 目录初始化** — Docusaurus 3.x 项目脚手架\\n   - `docusaurus.config.ts` — 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件）\\n   - `sidebars.ts` — 侧边栏导航结构\\n   - `package.json` — 依赖声明与脚本\\n   - `tsconfig.json` — TypeScript 配置\\n   - `babel.config.js` — Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求）\\n\\n2. **文档内容迁移与组织** — 将现有散落文档整合到 Docusaurus 结构中\\n   - `docs/overview/` — 项目简介、架构概览、快速开始\\n   - `docs/architecture/` — 各模块 design.md（router、workloadmanager、session-store、session-routing、sandbox-orchestration、deployment、ci-cd、code-execution、cli-toolkit、python-sdk、integrations、idle-cleanup）\\n   - `docs/api/` — API 参考（workloadmanager REST API、client-go 库）\\n   - `docs/guides/` — 部署指南、开发指南、贡献指南\\n   - `docs/specs/` — 各模块 spec.md（规范文档）\\n\\n3. **主题与样式**\\n   - Infima 默认主题定制（AgentCube 品牌色、Logo）\\n   - 代码块语法高亮（Go、Python、YAML、Bash、JSON）\\n   - Mermaid 图表渲染支持（架构图、流程图）\\n   - Admonition 组件使用规范（note、tip、warning、danger、info）\\n\\n4. **插件与集成**\\n   - `@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs` — 文档内容（内置）\\n   - `@docusaurus/plugin-content-pages` — 独立页面（内置）\\n   - `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid` — Mermaid 图表渲染\\n   - `@docusaurus/plugin-ideal-image` — 图片优化（可选）\\n\\n5. **构建与部署**\\n   - `npm run start` — 本地开发服务器（热重载）\\n   - `npm run build` — 生产构建\\n   - `npm run deploy` — 部署到 GitHub Pages\\n   - `.github/workflows/docs.yml` — CI 文档构建与部署 workflow\\n\\n6. **Makefile 目标**\\n   - `make docs-dev` — 启动本地文档... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n23: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897520965,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbdab2c001TuOyBmzEXLwZAv\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc90fb001qZJuu6w2F2bNaN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":38846,\"input\":35293,\"output\":3459,\"reasoning\":94,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.015606871}}\n24: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897522393,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbdb0d6001OGWLfRm5wCNkdK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbdab67001GYbjGNyCZGvgwV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n25: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775897525800,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbdb1e6001cks1XEXcibyKLJ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbdab67001GYbjGNyCZGvgwV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Written `changes/AR-042/proposal.md` with:\\n\\n- **Purpose** — Centralize scattered design/spec docs into a searchable, navigable Docusaurus site\\n- **Scope** — Docusaurus 3.x scaffolding, content migration from existing `design.md`/`spec.md` files, Mermaid support, CI/CD workflow, Makefile targets\\n- **Impact Analysis** — New `docs/` directory, Makefile additions, `.github/workflows/docs.yml`, dependencies on Node.js 20+ and Docusaurus npm packages\\n- **Alternatives Considered** — Docusaurus vs MkDocs vs Hugo (selected Docusaurus per project tech stack), manual vs auto-import vs link-only content strategy, Algolia vs local search, monorepo vs separate repo\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775897525798,\"end\":1775897525798}}}\n26: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897525823,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbdbe290013JSJ54KW9b79el\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbdab67001GYbjGNyCZGvgwV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":39050,\"input\":38865,\"output\":172,\"reasoning\":13,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.011032175}}\n27: \n\n(End of file - total 27 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"EXIT_CODE: 0\nSTDOUT:\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897426143,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc38db001ciaDlRH3VKkuIe\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc3115001QO9s6yMDYH8y34\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897430238,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bbc3f02001uESyZ6exTlc84V\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bbc3115001QO9s6yMDYH8y34\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28443cfd4ffewamynEkBK0sh0p\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_107b913751a1420fb29fa6b2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z</path>\\n<type>directory</type>\\n<entries>\\n.github/\\n.pytest_cache/\\n.sdd_prompt.md\\nagentd\\nbin/\\nchanges/\\nci-cd/\\ncli-toolkit/\\nclient-go/\\ncmd/\\ncode-execution/\\ncoverage.out\\ndelta-spec.md\\ndeployment/\\ndesign.md\\ndocker/\\nexampl