/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\\n34:   Sand... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n19: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897725658,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0cac9001k9VUFgS7PObYWg\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc0af63001hXemJ4VhKAiEXg\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":37686,\"input\":37516,\"output\":146,\"reasoning\":24,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.010635086}}\n20: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897726836,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0cf71001fnWZEYS4ulsivA\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc0caf0001aVr2JD3YBCAnSn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n21: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897728584,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0d2c8001DgLxMF9JDvWO0K\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc0caf0001aVr2JD3YBCAnSn\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_619a817f008546ff878472db\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — Makefile 构建目标体系\\n2: # AR-033: Unified build, test, docker, lint, helm, and python targets\\n3: \\n4: # ==============================================================================\\n5: # Variables and Configuration\\n6: # ==============================================================================\\n7: \\n8: TAG        ?= latest\\n9: REGISTRY   ?= agentcube\\n10: GOOS       ?= $(shell go env GOOS)\\n11: GOARCH     ?= $(shell go env GOARCH)\\n12: BIN_DIR    ?= bin\\n13: LDFLAGS    ?= -s -w\\n14: VERBOSE    ?=\\n15: \\n16: # Go binaries\\n17: GO_BINARIES := router workloadmanager agentd picod\\n18: \\n19: # Docker images (name -> Dockerfile mapping)\\n20: DOCKER_AGENTCUBE_DOCKERFILE := docker/Dockerfile\\n21: DOCKER_ROUTER_DOCKERFILE    := docker/Dockerfile.router\\n22: DOCKER_PICOD_DOCKERFILE     := docker/Dockerfile.picod\\n23: DOCKER_IMAGES               := agentcube router picod\\n24: \\n25: # Helm chart path\\n26: HELM_CHART_DIR := manifests/charts/base\\n27: \\n28: # Python paths\\n29: PYTHON_SDK_DIR  := python-sdk\\n30: PYTHON_CLI_DIR  := cmd/cli\\n31: \\n32: # ==============================================================================\\n33: # Verbosity helper\\n34: # ==============================================================================\\n35: \\n36: ifeq ($(VERBOSE),1)\\n37:   V =\\n38:   Q =\\n39: else\\n40:   V = @\\n41:   Q = @\\n42: endif\\n43: \\n44: # ========================... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n22: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897729806,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0d6d20017h1qrcpTf6Zlhi\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc0caf0001aVr2JD3YBC