* `CodeInterpreter` SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` and `metav1.ObjectMeta`, and implement `runtime.Object` via `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\\n17: \\n18: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter has status subresource enabled\\n19: - **GIVEN** the `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker is present on the `CodeInterpreter` type\\n20: - **WHEN** `controller-gen crd` generates the CRD YAML\\n21: - **THEN** the resulting CRD SHALL include `/status` as a subresource endpo... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897710972,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc08cbc001Etb5WYTGN8HoM2\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_a3a85e5edc4740cbacc199f7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-010: Router 会话管理 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，在 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的基础上，扩展 SessionManager 接口、实现 Redis/Valkey Store 后端、激活 Informer 事件处理器、引入会话生命周期 GC，并增强代理流程的会话感知能力。本变更是对 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的下游消费方，同时依赖 session-store spec 中定义的存储契约。\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: SessionManager 接口扩展\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中扩展 `SessionManager` 接口，新增以下方法：\\n12: \\n13: ```go\\n14: type SessionManager interface {\\n15:     // 现有方法（AR-009）\\n16:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n17: \\n18:     // 新增方法（AR-010）\\n19:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n20:     UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n21:     DeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\\n22:     UpdateLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\\n23:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n24: }\\n25: ```\\n26: \\n27: `CreateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.StoreSandbox` 将会话元数据写入存储后端。\\n28: \\n29: `UpdateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.UpdateSandbox` 更新已存在会话的元数据。\\n30: \\n31: `DeleteSession` SHALL 调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 删除会话及关联索引。\\n32: \\n33: `UpdateLastActivity` SH... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775897711039,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc091b1001ZJ7zJlvV5W5Ayb\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc07108001jhvVz5yzl5iQS1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":19389,\"input\":19074,\"output\":228,\"reasoning\":87,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.005784489}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775897714149,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc09de20019oQFWSZdIn4MPE\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc091d900186194x2Wp0Ci1K\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897715865,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0a010001egiG1BOs3W5zZ7\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc091d900186194x2Wp0Ci1K\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_e87177c83329471c9ff7384b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** docs\\n4: **Language:** TypeScript\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## Purpose\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。当前项目文档散落在各模块的 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 等文件中，缺乏统一的导航、搜索和版本管理能力。目标是提供一个可本地预览、可 CI 构建、可部署到 GitHub Pages 的结构化文档站，降低新贡献者的入门门槛，提升项目可维护性。\\n10: \\n11: ## Scope\\n12: \\n13: ### In Scope\\n14: \\n15: 1. **docs/ 目录初始化** — Docusaurus 3.x 项目脚手架\\n16:    - `docusaurus.config.ts` — 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件）\\n17:    - `sidebars.ts` — 侧边栏导航结构\\n18:    - `package.json` — 依赖声明与脚本\\n19:    - `tsconfig.json` — TypeScript 配置\\n20:    - `babel.config.js` — Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求）\\n21: \\n22: 2. **文档内容迁移与组织** — 将现有散落文档整合到 Docusaurus 结构中\\n23:    - `docs/overview/` — 项目简介、架构概览、快速开始\\n24:    - `docs/architecture/` — 各模块 design.md（router、workloadmanager、session-store、session-routing、sandbox-orchestration、deployment、ci-cd、code-execution、cli-toolkit、python-sdk、integrations、idle-cleanup）\\n25:    - `docs/api/` — API 参考（workloadmanager REST API、client-go 库）\\n26:    - `docs/guides/` — 部署指南、开发指南、贡献指南\\n27:    - `docs/specs/` — 各模块 spec.md（规范文档）\\n28: \\n29: 3. **主题与样式**\\n30:    - Infima 默认主题定制（AgentCube 品牌色、Logo）\\n31:    - 代码块语法高亮（Go、Python、YAML、Bash、JSON）\\n32:    - Mermaid 图表渲染支持（架构图、流程图）\\n33:    - Admonition 组件使用规范（note、tip、warning、danger、info）\\n34: \\n35: 4. **插件与集成**\\n36:    - `@do... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897717229,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc0a526001Zr2e1Cc0rRIc5Y\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc091d900186194x2Wp0Ci1K\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28442396fffeYAYu7CLqKnJbSn\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_7f159d5db72c4fa4baf95382\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"f