"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc36de5001R2QkDbDOzJj4sq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc361990013fLYSD85PJds6n\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_9829d199cd8742229f1b3ee8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-040: Python SDK/CLI 单元测试 — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. Architecture\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\\n6: \\n7: This AR covers comprehensive Python unit tests for the `agentcube-sdk` package (`sdk-python/`). The SDK provides high-level Python clients for creating Code Interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane), plus invoking AgentRuntime workloads.\\n8: \\n9: ### 1.2 Scope\\n10: \\n11: | Module | File | Lines | Test File | Status |\\n12: |--------|------|-------|-----------|--------|\\n13: | `agentcube/code_interpreter.py` | `CodeInterpreterClient` | 161 | `tests/test_code_interpreter.py` | **Partial** — 635 lines, but 3 methods missing `test_` prefix (won't run) |\\n14: | `agentcube/agent_runtime.py` | `AgentRuntimeClient` | 79 | `tests/test_agent_runtime.py` | **Good** — 837 lines |\\n15: | `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` | 96 | `tests/test_control_plane.py` | **Good** — 370 lines |\\n16: | `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` | 176 | `tests/test_data_plane.py` | **Good** — 641 lines |\\n17: | `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` | 80 | `tests/test_agent_runtime.py` | **Good** |\\n18: | `agentcube/exceptions.py` | Exception classes | 21 | `tests/test_exceptions.py` | **Good** — 77 lines |\\n19: | `agentcu... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897901271,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc374d3001oVd01z1KE8AF6X\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc361990013fLYSD85PJds6n\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_e36eee4184ce4e90868abe82\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\\n2: \\n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\\n5: \\n6: ## Purpose\\n7: \\n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\\n11: \\n12: ## Tech Stack\\n13: \\n14: | Layer | Technology |\\n15: |-------|-----------|\\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\\n24: \\n25: ## Architecture\\n26: \\n27: ```\\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\\n34:   Sand... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897903154,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc37a06001CFkXVEgMvGG4Eh\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc361990013fLYSD85PJds6n\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_7f167dabaab94f59b5423e14\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-036 — Dify 插件集成\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: 为 AgentCube 实现 Dify 平台插件集成，使 Dify 用户能够直接在 Agent 工作流中调用 AgentCube 的代码解释器（Code Interpreter）能力。该插件遵循 Dify 插件规范，提供工具提供者（Tool Provider）注册、参数模式声明、凭证校验和工具调用委托，将 Dify 的工具调用请求转发至 AgentCube SDK 的 `CodeInterpreterClient`。\\n6: \\n7: 同时提供 PCAP Analyzer 示例应用，展示如何在 FastAPI + LangChain/LangGraph 架构中使用 AgentCube 沙箱进行文件分析（上传、脚本生成、执行、重试、报告生成），并配套 Docker 容器化和 Kubernetes 部署配置。\\n8: \\n9: ## Scope\\n10: \\n11: ### In Scope\\n12: \\n13: 1. **Dify 插件核心文件**（`integrations/dify-plugin/`）\\n14: \\n15:    | 文件 | 说明 |\\n16:    |------|------|\\n17:    | `main.py` | 插件入口：`Plugin(DifyPluginEnv(MAX_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=120)).run()` |\\n18:    | `manifest.yaml` | 根插件清单：元数据、工具提供者注册、资源权限、Runner 声明 |\\n19:    | `provider/agentcube.yaml` | 工具提供者描述符：identity、工具列表、Python 入口 |\\n20:    | `provider/agentcube.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterProvider` — 凭证校验骨架 |\\n21:    | `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.yaml` | 工具参数模式（router_url、workload_manager_url、language、code、command、session_id、session_reuse、code_interpreter_id） |\\n22:    | `tools/agentcube-code-interpreter.py` | `AgentcubeCodeInterpreterTool` — `_invoke` 委托给 `execute()`，调用 `agentcube.CodeInterpreterClient` |\\n23:    | `requirements.txt` | 依赖：`dify-plugin>=0.4.2,<0.5.0` + `agentcube-sdk>=0.0.10` |\\n24:    | `GUIDE.md`, `README.md`, `PRIVACY.md`, `.difyignore` | 文档与打包配置 |\\n25: \\n26: 2. **工具提供者实现**\\n27:    - `AgentcubeCodeInterp... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897905415,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc380b7001xpP0Qee54Af2hE\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc361990013fLYSD85PJds6n\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_0ef58af417254063a7ec8111\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 — Tasks\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** `cmd/cli` | **Language:** Python | **Size:** M\\n4: **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `delta-spec.md`\\n5: \\n6: ---\\n7: \\n8: ## T-1: InvokeRuntime class skeleton + constructor\\n9: \\n10: - [ ] Create `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` with `InvokeRuntime` class\\n11: - [ ] Implement `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \\\"agentcube\\\")` setting `self.verbose` and `self.provider`\\n12: - [ ] Add `InvokeRuntime` export to `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\\n13: - [ ] Write test: constructor sets `verbose` and `provider` correctly (default and explicit values)\\n14: \\n15: ## T-2: InvokeRuntime._validate_invoke_prerequisites\\n16: \\n17: - [ ] Implement `_validate_invoke_prerequisites(workspace_path: Path) -> tuple[AgentMetadata, str, str]`\\n18: - [ ] Load metadata via `MetadataService`; raise `ValueError` if `agent_id` or `agent_endpoint` is missing\\n19: - [ ] Return `(metadata, agent_id, endpoint)` tuple\\n20: - [ ] Wr