功路径\\n21: \\n22: #### Scenario: 成功创建 AgentRuntime Sandbox\\n23: \\n24: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\\\"AgentRuntime\\\", Name, Namespace 已填）\\n25:   AND DynamicClient 已配置\\n26:   AND AgentRuntime CR 模板存在于目标 namespace\\n27:   AND Store 可写\\n28:   AND Reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce 可正常返回 channel\\n29: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context)` 被调用\\n30: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\\n31:   AND 响应体包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\\n32:   AND AgentRuntime CR 已创建到集群\\n3... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897915597,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc3ac450014aksxc1sjDt10J\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_7f779f483fcc4f29b124336b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/ci-cd/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube CI/CD — Design\\n2: \\n3: Sources: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/.github/workflows/`, `/tmp/agentcube-ref/test/`, and (for Make targets) `/tmp/agentcube-ref/Makefile`.\\n4: \\n5: ## GitHub Actions workflows (summary table)\\n6: \\n7: | Filename | Workflow `name` | Trigger events | Path filters (dorny/paths-filter or notes) | Jobs | Key steps | Env vars (job/step) | Secrets |\\n8: |----------|-----------------|----------------|---------------------------------------------|------|-----------|---------------------|---------|\\n9: | `main.yml` | Agentcube CI Workflow | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-*` | *(none)* | `build` | Checkout; Docker Buildx setup; verify Docker; `make docker-build` | — | — |\\n10: | `e2e.yml` | Agentcube E2E Tests | `pull_request` → `main`, `release-