wServer coerces to 1000\\n21: }\\n22: ```\\n23: \\n24: ### CLI flags (`cmd/router/main.go`)\\n25: \\n26: | Flag | Default |\\n27: |------|---------|\\n28: | `-port` | `8080` |\\n29: | `-enable-tls` | `false` |\\n30: | `-tls-cert` | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n31: | `-tls-key` | `\\\"\\\"` |\\n32: | `-debug` | `false` |\\n33: | `-max-concurrent-requests` | `1000` (0 means unlimited per flag help; `NewServer` still sets default 1000 when `<= 0`) |\\n34: \\n35: ### Server struct\\n36: \\n37: ```go\\n38: type Server struct {\\n39:     config         *Config\\n40:     engine         *gin.Engine\\n41:     httpServer     *http.Server\\n42:     sessionManager SessionManager\\n43:     storeClient    store.Store\\n44:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\\n45:     jwtManag... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775897918046,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc3b61c0014KFCxCalDwS00f\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc38ef1001tJX5AWujI7CRX7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2843cba31ffeB5jipUyIoDGq0I\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_c4857c8708ba497ab0ecfb8c\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/idle-cleanup/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Idle Cleanup — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Module\\n4: \\n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see root `go.mod` in sandbox-orchestration design).\\n6: \\n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd`\\n8: \\n9: ### Time threshold\\n10: \\n11: ```go\\n12: var SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\\n13: ```\\n14: \\n15: Idle expiration: `expirationTime := lastActivity.Add(SessionExpirationTimeout)`; delete when `time.Now().After(expirationTime)`.\\n16: \\n17: ### Annotation key\\n18: \\n19: The r