sts/runtime/test_status_runt... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n10: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775898228346,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc8765e001y6cNcsjX3uzq5e\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc85ffd001M8IBwdvHldbGof\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":18176,\"input\":17918,\"output\":226,\"reasoning\":32,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.005371326}}\n11: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775898229583,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc87b4c001KPgtVKkx3eQ3DT\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc876900016I51FPSW8YM6Wv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775898231613,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc87fb3001CwjJTnoWgPmVlk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc876900016I51FPSW8YM6Wv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_29d80802cc5a49e294b375bb\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. Architecture\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\\n6: \\n7: This AR establishes a Docusaurus 3.x documentation site for AgentCube, providing versioned documentation, multi-language support (en/zh), search, and automated CI/CD deployment. The docs site serves as the primary developer and user-facing documentation for the Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform.\\n8: \\n9: ### 1.2 Scope\\n10: \\n11: | Component | Description | Status |\\n12: |-----------|-------------|--------|\\n13: | Docusaurus 3.x project scaffold | `docs/` directory with full site configuration | **New** |\\n14: | Documentation content structure | Organized docs by audience and topic | **New** |\\n15: | Versioned documentation | Docusaurus versioning for release docs | **New** |\\n16: | Multi-language (i18n) | English + Simplified Chinese | **New** |\\n17: | Search integration | Algolia DocSearch or local search | **New** |\\n18: | CI/CD deployment | GitHub Pages or custom domain via GitHub Actions | **New** |\\n19: | Custom theme configuration | AgentCube branding, colors, logo | **New** |\\n20: | MDX support | Interactive docs with React components | **New** |\\n21: \\n22: ### 1.3 System Context\\n23: \\n24: ```\\n25: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n26: │                    Docusaurus 3.x Site                        │\\n27: │      ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n13: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1775898231673,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc8836c001i3OUDck0CTkvHY\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc876900016I51FPSW8YM6Wv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":20621,\"input\":20507,\"output\":71,\"reasoning\":43,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":0}},\"cost\":0.005848146}}\n14: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1775898233399,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc88a35001iHCh1seGvnjnbe\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc8838e001blADQCbz8sjLEY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"snapshot\":\"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775898306483,\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7bc89074001Uu6VT7BJm2eV25\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7bc8838e001blADQCbz8sjLEY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_26ffad6fedf7410c8c820657\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Tasks\\n\\n> **Module:** docs\\n> **Language:** TypeScript\\n> **Size:** M\\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n> **Reference:** `docs/design.md`, `changes/AR-042/design.md`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## T1. 初始化 Docusaurus 项目骨架\\n\\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `docs/` 目录创建 `package.json`，声明依赖：\\n  - `@docusaurus/core ^3.7.0`\\n  - `@docusaurus/preset-classic ^3.7.0`\\n  - `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases ^3.7.0`\\n  - `@docusaurus/tsconfig ^3.7.0`\\n  - `@docusaurus/types ^3.7.0`\\n  - `@mdx-js/react ^3.0.0`\\n  - `clsx ^2.0.0`\\n  - `prism-react-renderer ^2.3.0`\\n  - `react ^19.0.0`\\n  - `react-dom ^19.0.0`\\n- [ ] 1.2 创建 `babel.config.js`（Docusaurus 默认配置）\\n- [ ] 1.3 创建 `tsconfig.json`，继承 `@docusaurus/tsconfig`\\n- [ ] 1.4 创建 `docusaurus.config.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.1）：\\n  - 站点元信息（title, tagline, favicon, url, baseUrl）\\n  - i18n 配置（en/zh）\\n  - classic preset（docs, blog, theme）\\n  - themeConfig（navbar, footer, prism, algolia placeholder）\\n  - Mermaid 支持（`markdown.mermaid: true`, `themes: ['@docusaurus/theme-mermaid']`）\\n  - 严格模式（`onBrokenLinks: 'throw'`, `onBrokenAssets: 'throw'`）\\n- [ ] 1.5 创建 `sidebars.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.2），定义 7 个分类：\\n  - Getting Started, Architecture, User Guide, API Reference, Integrations, Operations, Contributing\\n- [ ] 1.6 运行 `npm install` 确认依赖安装成功\\n\\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npx docusaurus --version` 输出 3.x；`npx tsc --noEmit` 无类型错误\\n\\n---\\n\\n## T2. 创建目录结构与分类元数据\\n\\n- [ ] 2.1 创建 `docs/docs/` 目录结构（参考 `docs/design.md` §1.5）：\\n  - `getting-started/`（installation, quick-start, configuration）\\n  - `architecture/`（overview, components, session-routing, sandbox-lifecycle）\\n  - `user-guide/`（code-i... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\