{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899000463,"sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd438ce0013QSp3D0vt2OOgp","messageID":"msg_d7bd42dca001KnELOQ4Ulz7Hpz","sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_dec4ea51b61a40ed86f165e7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。将散落在各模块 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 中的文档整合为具有统一导航、搜索和渲染能力的结构化文档站，支持本地预览、CI 构建和 GitHub Pages 部署。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: Docusaurus 项目脚手架初始化\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `docs/` 目录下初始化完整的 Docusaurus 3.x TypeScript 项目结构，包含以下核心配置文件：\n12: \n13: | 文件 | 用途 |\n14: |------|------|\n15: | `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件、Mermaid 支持） |\n16: | `docs/sidebars.ts` | 侧边栏导航结构 |\n17: | `docs/package.json` | 依赖声明与 npm 脚本 |\n18: | `docs/tsconfig.json` | TypeScript 编译配置 |\n19: | `docs/babel.config.js` | Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求） |\n20: \n21: **`docusaurus.config.ts` 必须包含：**\n22: - `title`: `\"AgentCube\"`\n23: - `tagline`: `\"Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\"`\n24: - `url`: `\"https://volcano-sh.github.io\"`\n25: - `baseUrl`: `\"/agentcube/\"`\n26: - `themeConfig`: 导航栏（logo、链接）、页脚、Mermaid 配置\n27: - `presets`: `@docusaurus/preset-classic` 启用 docs、blog（禁用）、pages\n28: - `markdown`: 启用 `mermaid` 支持\n29: \n30: **`package.json` 必须声明的依赖：**\n31: - `@docusaurus/core`: `\"^3.7.0\"`\n32: - `@docusaurus/preset-classic`: `\"^3.7.0\"`\n33: - `@docusaurus/theme-mermaid`: `\"^3.7.0\"`\n34: - `@mdx-js/react`: `\"^3.0.0\"`\n35: - `react`: `\"^18.0.0\"`\n36: - `react-dom`: `\"^18.0.0\"`\n37: - `typescript`: `\"^5.0.0\"`\n38: \n39: **npm scripts 必须包含：**\n40: - `start`: `\"docusaurus start\"`\n41: - `build`: `\"docusaurus build\"`\n42: - `swizzle`: `\"docusaurus swizzle\"`\n43: - `deploy`: `\"docusaurus deploy\"`\n44: - `clear`: `\"docusaurus clear\"`\n45: - `serve`: `\"docusaurus serve\"`\n46: - `typecheck`: `\"tsc\"`\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: 项目脚手架文件完整\n49: \n50: - **GIVEN** `docs/` 目录已初始化\n51: - **WHEN** 检查 `docs/` 根目录\n52: - **THEN** 存在 `docusaurus.config.ts`、`sidebars.ts`、`package.json`、`tsconfig.json`、`babel.config.js`\n53: \n54: #### Scenario: package.json 依赖声明完整\n55: \n56: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` 已编写\n57: - **WHEN** 解析 `dependencies` 和 `devDependencies`\n58: - **THEN** 包含 `@docusaurus/core`、`@docusaurus/preset-classic`、`@docusaurus/theme-mermaid`、`react`、`react-dom`、`typescript`\n59: \n60: #### Scenario: npm scripts 包含标准命令\n61: \n62: - **GIVEN** `docs/package.json` 已编写\n63: - **WHEN** 检查 `scripts` 字段\n64: - **THEN** 包含 `start`、`build`、`deploy`、`serve`、`typecheck` 脚本\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: docusaurus.config.ts 站点元数据正确\n67: \n68: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` 已编写\n69: - **WHEN** 检查配置对象\n70: - **THEN** `title` 为 `\"AgentCube\"`，`tagline` 包含 `\"sandbox orchestration\"`，`url` 为 `\"https://volcano-sh.github.io\"`，`baseUrl` 为 `\"/agentcube/\"`\n71: \n72: #### Scenario: Mermaid 插件已启用\n73: \n74: - **GIVEN** `docusaurus.config.ts` 已编写\n75: - **WHEN** 检查 `markdown.mermaid` 配置\n76: - **THEN** `mermaid` 字段存在且配置了 `theme`（如 `\"default\"`）\n77: \n78: ---\n79: \n80: ### Requirement: 侧边栏导航结构\n81: \n82: The system SHALL 在 `docs/sidebars.ts` 中定义完整的文档导航结构，覆盖以下分类：\n83: \n84: | 分类 ID | 显示名称 | 内容 |\n85: |---------|----------|------|\n86: | `overview` | Overview | 项目简介、架构概览、快速开始 |\n87: | `architecture` | Architecture | 12 个模块的设计文档 |\n88: | `api` | API Reference | WorkloadManager REST API、client-go 库 |\n89: | `guides` | Guides | 部署指南、开发指南、贡献指南 |\n90: | `specs` | Specifications | 各模块的 spec 文档 |\n91: \n92: 每个分类 SHALL 使用 Docusaurus 的 `category` 类型，通过 `docId` 或 `type: 'autogenerated', dirName` 自动生成。\n93: \n94: #### Scenario: 侧边栏包含所有五大分类\n95: \n96: - **GIVEN** `sidebars.ts` 已编写\n97: - **WHEN** 解析 `sidebars` 对象\n98: - **THEN** 包含 `overview`、`architecture`、`api`、`guides`、`specs` 五个分类\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: architecture 分类包含所有模块入口\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 635. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 项目建立基于 Docusaurus 3.x 的文档站点框架，集中管理项目的架构设计、API 参考、部署指南、开发手册和用户文档。将散落在各模块 `design.md`、`spec.md`、`README.md` 中的文档整合为具有统一导航、搜索和渲染能力的结构化文档站，支持本地预览、CI 构建和 GitHub Pages 部署。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Docusaurus 项目脚手架初始化\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `docs/` 目录下初始化完整的 Docusaurus 3.x TypeScript 项目结构，包含以下核心配置文件：\n\n| 文件 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| `docs/docusaurus.config.ts` | 站点配置（标题、URL、主题、插件、Mermaid 支持） |\n| `docs/sidebars.ts` | 侧边栏导航结构 |\n| `docs/package.json` | 依赖声明与 npm 脚本 |\n| `docs/tsconfig.json` | TypeScript 编译配置 |\n| `docs/babel.config.js` | Babel 配置（Docusaurus 要求） |\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775899000450,"end":1775899000461}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899001667,"sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd43f12001D0fGq886FnTikc","messageID":"msg_d7bd42dca001KnELOQ4Ulz7Hpz","sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_507ed81ab0634be6b46e2ca2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/intro.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/intro.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: sidebar_position: 1\n3: title: Introduction\n4: description: Overview of AgentCube, a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\n5: keywords: [agentcube, kubernetes, sandbox, ai-agents, orchestration]\n6: ---\n7: \n8: # Introduction\n9: \n10: AgentCube is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform** designed for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their complete lifecycle from creation to cleanup.\n11: \n12: ## What is AgentCube?\n13: \n14: AgentCube provides a secure, scalable infrastructure for running AI agent workloads in isolated environments. Built on Kubernetes Custom Resource Definitions (CRDs) and the controller-runtime framework, it integrates seamlessly with existing Kubernetes infrastructure.\n15: \n16: ## Key Features\n17: \n18: - **Sandbox Isolation**: Each AI agent runs in its own isolated pod with configurable resource limits, network policies, and security contexts\n19: - **Session-Aware Routing**: Intelligent HTTP routing with session persistence ensures traffic reaches the correct sandbox instance\n20: - **Code Interpreter**: Built-in code execution engine supporting multiple languages with safe execution guarantees\n21: - **Agent Runtime**: Full lifecycle management including automatic scaling, health monitoring, and graceful shutdown\n22: - **Multi-Language SDK**: Python SDK and CLI for easy integration, plus RESTful APIs for custom integrations\n23: \n24: ## Architecture Overview\n25: \n26: AgentCube consists of several core components:\n27: \n28: ```\n29: Client / SDK / CLI\n30:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n31:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n32:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n33:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n34:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n35:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n36:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ### Core Components\n40: \n41: | Component | Description |\n42: |-----------|-------------|\n43: | **Router** | Session-aware HTTP proxy that routes requests to the correct sandbox |\n44: | **WorkloadManager** | Kubernetes controller that manages sandbox lifecycle |\n45: | **Session Store** | Redis/Valkey backend for session state and routing information |\n46: | **PicoD** | Optional daemon running inside sandbox pods for code execution |\n47: | **Agentd** | Idle cleanup controller that reclaims unused sandboxes |\n48: \n49: ## Who Should Use AgentCube?\n50: \n51: - **AI Platform Engineers**: Building multi-tenant AI agent platforms on Kubernetes\n52: - **ML Engineers**: Needing isolated code execution environments for AI workloads\n53: - **DevOps Teams**: Managing sandbox infrastructure at scale\n54: - **Security Teams**: Requiring strong isolation between agent workloads\n55: \n56: ## Getting Started\n57: \n58: Ready to try AgentCube? Jump to our [Quick Start guide](./getting-started/quick-start.md) to get up and running in 5 minutes.\n59: \n60: For a deeper understanding of the system, check out the [Architecture Overview](./architecture/overview.md).\n\n(End of file - total 60 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nsidebar_position: 1\ntitle: Introduction\ndescription: Overview of AgentCube, a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents\nkeywords: [agentcube, kubernetes, sandbox, ai-agents, orchestration]\n---\n\n# Introduction\n\nAgentCube is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform** designed for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their complete lifecycle from creation to cleanup.\n\n## What is AgentCube?\n\nAgentCube provides a secure, scalable infrastructure for running AI agent workloads in isolated environments. Built on Kubernetes Custom Resource Definitions (CRDs) and the controller-runtime framework, it integrates seamlessly with existing Kubernetes infrastructure.\n\n## Key Features\n\n- **Sandbox Isolation**: Each AI agent runs in its own isolated pod with configurable resource limits, network policies, and security contexts\n- **Session-Aware Routing**: Intelligent HTTP routing with session persistence ensures traffic reaches the correct sandbox instance\n- **Code Interpreter**: Built-in code execution engine supporting multiple languages with safe execution guarantees","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/docs/intro.md","time":{"start":1775899001656,"end":1775899001666}}}}
