{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899022784,"sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","part":{"id":"prt_d7bd49136001aoTe4JxsR9qQjI","messageID":"msg_d7bd48927001SNVLT36D6No7vc","sessionID":"ses_2842d085bffed8MeVZzVoGA6fX","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_e2e9a17b182a4088a04d6795","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** docs\n4: > **Language:** TypeScript\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `docs/design.md`, `changes/AR-042/design.md`\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## T1. 初始化 Docusaurus 项目骨架\n12: \n13: - [ ] 1.1 在 `docs/` 目录创建 `package.json`，声明依赖：\n14:   - `@docusaurus/core ^3.7.0`\n15:   - `@docusaurus/preset-classic ^3.7.0`\n16:   - `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases ^3.7.0`\n17:   - `@docusaurus/tsconfig ^3.7.0`\n18:   - `@docusaurus/types ^3.7.0`\n19:   - `@mdx-js/react ^3.0.0`\n20:   - `clsx ^2.0.0`\n21:   - `prism-react-renderer ^2.3.0`\n22:   - `react ^19.0.0`\n23:   - `react-dom ^19.0.0`\n24: - [ ] 1.2 创建 `babel.config.js`（Docusaurus 默认配置）\n25: - [ ] 1.3 创建 `tsconfig.json`，继承 `@docusaurus/tsconfig`\n26: - [ ] 1.4 创建 `docusaurus.config.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.1）：\n27:   - 站点元信息（title, tagline, favicon, url, baseUrl）\n28:   - i18n 配置（en/zh）\n29:   - classic preset（docs, blog, theme）\n30:   - themeConfig（navbar, footer, prism, algolia placeholder）\n31:   - Mermaid 支持（`markdown.mermaid: true`, `themes: ['@docusaurus/theme-mermaid']`）\n32:   - 严格模式（`onBrokenLinks: 'throw'`, `onBrokenAssets: 'throw'`）\n33: - [ ] 1.5 创建 `sidebars.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.2），定义 7 个分类：\n34:   - Getting Started, Architecture, User Guide, API Reference, Integrations, Operations, Contributing\n35: - [ ] 1.6 运行 `npm install` 确认依赖安装成功\n36: \n37: **Verification:** `cd docs && npx docusaurus --version` 输出 3.x；`npx tsc --noEmit` 无类型错误\n38: \n39: ---\n40: \n41: ## T2. 创建目录结构与分类元数据\n42: \n43: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `docs/docs/` 目录结构（参考 `docs/design.md` §1.5）：\n44:   - `getting-started/`（installation, quick-start, configuration）\n45:   - `architecture/`（overview, components, session-routing, sandbox-lifecycle）\n46:   - `user-guide/`（code-interpreter, agent-runtime, cli, python-sdk）\n47:   - `api-reference/`（control-plane, data-plane, crds）\n48:   - `integrations/`（dify-plugin, langchain）\n49:   - `operations/`（deployment, monitoring, troubleshooting, security）\n50:   - `contributing/`（development, testing, release-process）\n51: - [ ] 2.2 为每个分类目录创建 `_category_.json`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.3）\n52: - [ ] 2.3 创建 `docs/src/css/custom.css`（AgentCube 品牌色覆盖）\n53: - [ ] 2.4 创建 `docs/src/pages/index.tsx`（首页骨架）\n54: - [ ] 2.5 创建 `docs/src/pages/index.module.css`（首页样式）\n55: - [ ] 2.6 创建 `docs/src/components/HomepageFeatures/`（首页特性组件）\n56: - [ ] 2.7 创建 `docs/img/` 目录，放置 logo.svg 和 favicon.ico 占位文件\n57: \n58: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功，无 broken links/assets 错误\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## T3. 编写 P0 核心文档内容\n63: \n64: - [ ] 3.1 编写 `docs/docs/intro.md`（项目概述，从 `project.md` 迁移）\n65: - [ ] 3.2 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md`（Helm 安装指南）\n66: - [ ] 3.3 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/quick-start.md`（5 分钟快速上手）\n67: - [ ] 3.4 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`（系统架构概览，含 Mermaid 图）\n68: - [ ] 3.5 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/code-interpreter.md`（Code Interpreter 使用指南）\n69: - [ ] 3.6 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/agent-runtime.md`（Agent Runtime 使用指南）\n70: \n71: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；所有 P0 文档可通过 `npm run serve` 本地预览\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## T4. 编写 P1 文档内容与 API 骨架\n76: \n77: - [ ] 4.1 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/configuration.md`（Helm values 参考）\n78: - [ ] 4.2 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/components.md`（组件详解）\n79: - [ ] 4.3 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md`（路由与会话管理）\n80: - [ ] 4.4 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/sandbox-lifecycle.md`（沙箱生命周期）\n81: - [ ] 4.5 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/cli.md`（CLI 命令参考）\n82: - [ ] 4.6 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/python-sdk.md`（Python SDK 参考）\n83: - [ ] 4.7 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md`（API 骨架）\n84: - [ ] 4.8 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md`（API 骨架）\n85: - [ ] 4.9 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md`（CRD 参考骨架）\n86: - [ ] 4.10 编写 `docs/docs/operations/deployment.md`（生产部署指南）\n87: - [ ] 4.11 编写 `docs/docs/operations/troubleshooting.md`（常见问题排查）\n88: - [ ] 4.12 编写 `docs/docs/operations/security.md`（认证、RBAC、网络策略）\n89: - [ ] 4.13 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/development.md`（开发指南）\n90: - [ ] 4.14 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/testing.md`（测试指南）\n91: - [ ] 4.15 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/release-process.md`（发布流程）\n92: - [ ] 4.16 创建 `docs/docs/integrations/dify-plugin.md`（骨架）\n93: - [ ] 4.17 创建 `docs/docs/integrations/langchain.md`（骨架）\n94: - [ ] 4.18 创建 `docs/docs/operations/monitoring.md`（骨架）\n95: \n96: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；所有文档 frontmatter 符合 schema（§2.4）\n97: \n98: ---\n99: \n100: ## T5. 自定义 MDX 组件\n101: \n102: - [ ] 5.1 创建 `docs/src/components/ApiEndpoint/index.tsx`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.5）：\n103:   - Props: `method`, `path`, `description`, `auth`\n104:   - 渲染 HTTP 方法徽章 + 路径 + 描述\n105: - [ ] 5.2 创建 `docs/src/components/K8sResource/index.tsx`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.5）：\n106:   - Props: `group`, `version`, `kind`, `scope`, `yamlExample`\n107:   - 渲染 CRD 信息卡片 + 可选 YAML 示例代码块\n108: - [ ] 5.3 为两个组件编写基础样式（CSS modules 或内联样式）\n109: - [ ] 5.4 在至少一个文档中使用 `ApiEndpoint` 组件验证渲染\n110: - [ ] 5.5 在至少一个文档中使用 `K8sResource` 组件验证渲染\n111: \n112: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；MDX 组件在 `npm run serve` 中正确渲染\n113: \n114: ---\n115: \n116: ## T6. i18n 多语言支持\n117: \n118: - [ ] 6.1 运行 `docusaurus write-translations --locale zh` 生成翻译基础文件\n119: - [ ] 6.2 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current.json`（分类/标签翻译）\n120: - [ ] 6.3 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-theme-classic/navbar.json`（导航栏翻译）\n121: - [ ] 6.4 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-theme-classic/footer.json`（页脚翻译）\n122: - [ ] 6.5 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/code.json`（UI 字符串翻译）\n123: - [ ] 6.6 翻译 P0 文档至中文：\n124:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/intro.md`\n125:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/getting-started/installation.md`\n126:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/getting-started/quick-start.md`\n127:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/architecture/overview.md`\n128:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/user-guide/code-interpreter.md`\n129:   - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/user-guide/agent-runtime.md`\n130: - [ ] 6.7 创建 `scripts/check-i18n.sh`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.5），检查翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n131: \n132: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；访问 `/zh/docs/` 显示中文内容；`bash scripts/check-i18n.sh` 覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n133: \n134: ---\n135: \n136: ## T7. CI/CD 流水线与部署\n137: \n138: - [ ] 7.1 创建 `.github/workflows/docs.yml`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.7）：\n139:   - PR 触发：`docs/**` 路径变更\n140:   - Node.js 20 环境，npm ci 缓存\n141:   - `npx tsc --noEmit` 类型检查\n142:   - `npm run build` 构建验证\n143:   - 链接检查（`npx check-links`）\n144:   - i18n 覆盖率检查\n145:   - 构建产物上传（`actions/upload-pages-artifact`）\n146: - [ ] 7.2 创建部署 job（`deploy`），仅在 `main` 分支触发：\n147:   - 使用 `actions/deploy-pages@v4`\n148:   - 配置 `permissions: pages: write, id-token: write`\n149:   - 配置 `environment: github-pages`\n150: - [ ] 7.3 在 `docs/package.json` 中添加 scripts：\n151:   - `start`: `docusaurus start`\n152:   - `build`: `docusaurus build`\n153:   - `serve`: `docusaurus serve`\n154:   - `deploy`: `docusaurus deploy`\n155:   - `clear`: `docusaurus clear`\n156:   - `typecheck`: `tsc --noEmit`\n157: - [ ] 7.4 创建 `docs/lighthouserc.json`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.4）\n158: - [ ] 7.5 在 Makefile 中添加 docs 相关 target：\n159:   - `make docs-build`: 构建文档站\n160:   - `docs-serve`: 启动本地开发服务器\n161:   - `docs-check`: 运行类型检查 + 构建 + 链接检查\n162: \n163: **Verification:** PR 修改 `docs/` 下文件触发 CI 并通过所有检查；`make docs-build` 成功\n164: \n165: ---\n166: \n167: ## T8. 搜索与版本管理\n168: \n169: - [ ] 8.1 安装 `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local ^0.48.0`（本地搜索 fallback）\n170: - [ ] 8.2 在 `docusaurus.config.ts` 中配置本地搜索插件\n171: - [ ] 8.3 配置 Algolia DocSearch placeholder（`appId`, `apiKey` 使用 TBD 占位）\n172: - [ ] 8.4 运行 `docusaurus docs:version 0.1.x` 创建首个版本快照\n173: - [ ] 8.5 验证 `versions.json` 包含 `[\"current\", \"0.1.x\"]`\n174: - [ ] 8.6 验证版本切换 dropdown 在 navbar 中正常工作\n175: - [ ] 8.7 创建 `docs/versioned_sidebars/version-0.1.x-sidebars.json`\n176: \n177: **Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；本地搜索可用；版本切换正常\n178: \n179: ---\n180: \n181: ## T9. 质量门禁与最终验证\n182: \n183: - [ ] 9.1 运行 `cd docs && npx tsc --noEmit` 确认无类型错误\n184: - [ ] 9.2 运行 `cd docs && npm run build` 确认构建成功\n185: - [ ] 9.3 运行 `cd docs && npm run serve` 手动验证所有页面渲染\n186: - [ ] 9.4 验证所有 P0/P1 文档内容完整且无 placeholder 文本\n187: - [ ] 9.5 验证 i18n 翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n188: - [ ] 9.6 验证 Mermaid 图表在文档中正确渲染\n189: - [ ] 9.7 验证 MDX 组件（ApiEndpoint, K8sResource）正常渲染\n190: - [ ] 9.8 验证本地搜索功能正常\n191: - [ ] 9.9 验证版本切换功能正常\n192: - [ ] 9.10 验证 CI workflow 文件语法正确（`act -j build --dryrun` 或 GitHub Actions lint）\n193: - [ ] 9.11 确认 `docs/.gitignore` 排除 `node_modules/`, `build/`, `.docusaurus/`\n194: \n195: **Verification:** 以上全部通过；`npm run build` exit code 0；无 broken links/assets 警告\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ## Task Dependencies\n200: \n201: ```\n202: T1 (项目骨架) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n203:   │                                                                          │\n204:   ▼                                                                          │\n205: T2 (目录结构) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n206:   │                                                                          │\n207:   ├──────────► T3 (P0 文档) ────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n208:   │                                                                          │\n209:   ├──────────► T4 (P1 文档 + API 骨架) ─────────────────────────────────────┤\n210:   │                                                                          │\n211:   ├──────────► T5 (MDX 组件) ───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n212:   │                                                                          │\n213:   ▼                                                                          │\n214: T6 (i18n) ←── T3, T4 ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n215:   │                                                                          │\n216:   ▼                                                                          │\n217: T7 (CI/CD) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n218:   │                                                                          │\n219:   ▼                                                                          │\n220: T8 (搜索 + 版本) ←── T2 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n221:   │                                                                          │\n222:   ▼                                                                          │\n223: T9 (质量门禁) ←── T3, T4, T5, T6, T7, T8 ───────────────────────────────────┘\n224: ```\n225: \n226: **Parallel execution:**\n227: - T3, T4, T5 可在 T2 完成后并行开发\n228: - T6 需 T3/T4 完成后开始（依赖英文文档）\n229: - T7 和 T8 可在 T2 完成后并行开发\n230: - T9 需所有前置任务完成\n231: \n232: ---\n233: \n234: ## Acceptance Criteria\n235: \n236: | # | Criterion | Verification Command |\n237: |---|-----------|---------------------|\n238: | AC1 | Docusaurus 项目可构建 | `cd docs && npm run build` exit 0 |\n239: | AC2 | TypeScript 类型检查通过 | `cd docs && npx tsc --noEmit` |\n240: | AC3 | 7 个文档分类完整 | `sidebars.ts` 包含所有分类 |\n241: | AC4 | P0 文档内容完整（6 篇） | `docs/docs/` 下文件存在且非空 |\n242: | AC5 | P1 文档内容完整（13 篇） | `docs/docs/` 下文件存在且非空 |\n243: | AC6 | 中文翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `bash scripts/check-i18n.sh` |\n244: | AC7 | Mer